{"word":"G4354 - προσλαλέω - proslaléō - pros-lal-eh'-o - Speak to","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσλαλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">proslaléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-lal-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Speak to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பேசு"},{"paragraph":"to speak to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G2980 - λαλέω - laléō - lal-eh'-o/2980\">G2980</a>; to <i>talk to</i>, that is, <i>converse with:</i> - speak to (with).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}